  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK882">
<l>vāḷpōl pakaivarai yañcaṟka vañcuka</l>
<l>kēḷpōl pakaivar toṭarpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fear not foes (who say they would cut) like a sword (but) fear the friendship of foes (who seemingly act) like relations.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
